column37:
Hi everyone,

I'm Jana, love being part of choirs and ensembles and love performing.
Classically trained in Piano and Mandolin, I've a broad area of musical ability and studied at ECU for my Bachelor of Education (Double degree in music and arts).
I'm also an IT site support Technician and work FIFO (Fly in, Fly out) every week so at this stage I can make every second rehearsal and will unfortunately miss a couple of performances. I work up north at an Iron Ore Mine Site at Roy Hill.

Will be great to sing with all of you!

Kind regards,
Jana
